{
  "page": "Goat boy",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Goat boy</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_of_Qaggaz\" title=\"House of Qaggaz\">House of Qaggaz</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>goat boy</b> is a deformed <a href=\"/index.php/Slave\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Slave\">slave</a> owned by <a href=\"/index.php/Yezzan_zo_Qaggaz\" title=\"Yezzan zo Qaggaz\">Yezzan zo Qaggaz</a>.  He is a part of Yezzan’s <a href=\"/index.php/Grotesquerie\" title=\"Grotesquerie\">grotesquerie</a>, one of Yezzan's \"<i>special treasures</i>\". \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Goat_boy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_the_goat_boy\" title=\"Category:Images of the goat boy\">Images of the goat boy</a></div>\n<p>The goat boy has twisted (deformed) hairy \"<a href=\"/index.php/Goat\" title=\"Goat\">goat</a>-legs.\" He is young and speaks the guttural sailor's pidgin called the <a href=\"/index.php/Trade_talk\" title=\"Trade talk\">trade talk</a>. Where Yezzan acquired him is not known.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Goat_boy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Goat_boy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Along with the rest of Yezzan's special treasures, the goat boy accompanies his master to the <a href=\"/index.php/Yunkish\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Yunkish\">Yunkish</a> encampment outside of <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>He performs during Yezzan's banquet for <a href=\"/index.php/Yurkhaz_zo_Yunzak\" title=\"Yurkhaz zo Yunzak\">Yurkhaz zo Yunzak</a>. He comes out and dances a grotesque jig, whilst one of Yurkhaz's <a href=\"/index.php/Slave\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Slave\">slaves</a> plays on a <a href=\"/index.php/Bone_flute\" title=\"Bone flute\">bone flute</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When Yezzan contracts the <a href=\"/index.php/Pale_mare\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Pale mare\">pale mare</a>, it falls to Yezzan's special treasures to attend to him as he is dying. The goat-legged boy hopes the <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">silver queen</a> will save them. <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Penny\" title=\"Penny\">Penny</a> escape before they can learn of the fate of Yezzan's grotesquerie. The fate of the goat boy is unknown.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Goat_boy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_47\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 47\">Chapter 47</a>, Tyrion X.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_25\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 25\">Chapter 25</a>, The Windblown.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_57\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 57\">Chapter 57</a>, Tyrion XI.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404205710\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.068 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.246 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 709/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10484/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4081/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument siz